i dont wat to grow up.i dont want things to change so much.i dont want to graduate or move or be alone.i want to have this stability and structure forever.all of the sudden im scared.ive got time but i dont want to have to ever say goodbye.i hate that word.c'mon tink i want some pixie dust.
im a selfish bitch.who doesnt get what she wants.o fuckin well.ill go pity myself and make adam smile.cuz i can cuz he's mine.nobody elses.

i hate thining about you so fuckin much. i hate that i still miss you.i hate how i cant go anywhere without thinking about you or something that we did or said or shared together. i miss holding you.i miss taking care of you.i hate missing being the one you ran to and.1736 steps from my house to yours?i hate feeling the memories.i dont want to remember.you were so beautiful.anytime anywhere.whether you were sleeping or crying or laughing.i loved all of it.i hate that i hurt you so much.1101 glenwillow lane.goddamnit."you were always the world to me" fuckin a sushi im so sorry.i hate that too. i hate that after all this time im still crying about you.by loving you so much i hurt you.all the movies we ever watched together,any cookie,boys kissing,music,cigarettes,blood,laughter.....all of it makes me think of you.cloves reming me of your house because your mom smoked them.checkers because of the shoelaces i gave you once for christmas.pink.sunrises because of that day tim spent the night and we went in search of a dennys.birthmarks.a unicorn giving a ride to a bumble bee, a poodle, and hawaii.sushi because its your nickname.oreos because your the only person i have ever met that leaves one on the bottom of the milk, drinks the milk and then eats the mush at the bottom.i ate a whole pack a few weeks ago and it made me cry.what you used to order at taco bell.all these pathetic things about you that i remember.all your favs.casablanca,sprite,britany spears,pink,colorful things,smiles,shopping,shoes,pictures...life.id still die for you.but ill never get the chance sadly.yeah i have moved on but sometimes i remember and need some time to think.you have a life that doesnt include me which is cool as long as your happy.i like my life and i no nothing will come of any of my pathetic rantings and im fine with that.oi my konstantine.im done.

wow all i fuckin have to say is that people fuckin suck sometimes and wow.i hate change.

got up early and went to adams to help him finish packing then took all of them to bart at 10:30 and his flight leaves at 4. i hate planes so yesterday i bought him a calling card so he can let me know he is ok.18 days without adam.shit.i miss him already.he was laughin at me cuz i wouldnt stop lookin at him this mornin. i hope he has fun though.oi i love germany. right now i want flowers,butterflies and coffee.the weather sucks ass so i get none of these.so today i will drown myself in mindess shit.tv,sims and laundry all sound nice.who knows maybe ill venture as far as blockbuster soon. i swear today is the only day im giving myself to be like this.wow  i have to take care of the baby on wed and i already can see how thats gonna go. im gonna get all pathetic, maybe cry but dance alot.she is so pretty and she loves flowers and being outside so thats where we'll be most of the day i bet.i love babies.and tell me aurora isnt a cool ass name.hmmm i need quiet time.

hmm i wanna hang tomorrow.who's doin what?

thus begins day one alone

well nothin all too fantastic these days.just been livin i guess. adam leaves for germany tomorrow:(which sux ass in case nobody knew.been fightin with my mom lately but i think things are pretty clear now..i tell her where i am and come home by 11 every night then she leaves me alone and askes no questions. i am gonna miss adam sooooo fuckin much....oi....ill just find shit to keep me busy...i dont wanna be alone cuz then ill think about him...miss him and then get all pathetic and not move till he comes home....so ok guys ready? new mission: called operation keep aly out of her house.up for it?

well ok havnt turned on ym computer in hella days. sorry bout that....but yeah anyways SCHOOLS OUT!!!! (for summer......)lol....im in a good mood...these past few days have been interesting.....day befor yesterday i learned how to longboard:) adam taught me at pulty...i felt soo cool cuz i have NEVER been able to stand on anything with wheels let alone actually MOVE...:) i think kt and marilyn were really proud of me...adam was too...he loves teachin me stuff...its so cute...then yesterday was really really really wierd.....i mean ok right after school adam and me went to la costa then napped in my car for 2 hours while we waited for everybody to come back from aloras house then when the got there marilyn gave me a flower :) and we put on stray cats and everybody was sing ing and some danced. it was funny. even this old guy was like bobbin his head as he walked to his car. then adam,tues,bretterz,marilyn will and eden and me went to the farmers market, got strawberries and then walked up to the rec center for drinks. i was fun...then i only got to see kt anessa fpr like 10 mins befor we all went over to bristow(tues stayed with them) it was cool cuz since bretterz got his license we were the drivers so we all split into the two cars and drove to bristow. the funniest part of that was when will and adam randomly jumped up and chased after this chick cuz she had a dollar hangin out of her pocket.they are so cute.they make me laugh.eden is so damn cool.she is the only one i know with the small child fascination like me...i love little kids and she kept going "o look at that one! isnt she cute will!i want her!"  i laughed alot:) then i found out my mom was in a car accident and i kinda freaked out. she is ok but her car is fucked....not even drivable anymore so yeah.then adam and i went back to his house and watched anastasia and then went on a hour long walk... we tried to call kt to give her an update but nooo she didnt answer her phone....lol...adam wont be able to go anywhere in this town without thinkin about me....hahaha....anyways today is graduation and im not sure if i am gonna go or not. i need something to do.

today i was thinking about alot of stuff randomly...upbeat style..not emo but still emo at heart...woot for bipolar abilities and i felt like writing a note to my adam and it ended up my detailed explaination of my life views...one quote i got from it was one of the most honest things i have ever written....

"i figured out why bubbles and clouds mean so much to me.they are as innocent and pure as you can get if you think about it. they never are stuck in one shape.they drift and go where ever they want. thats beautiful. i wanna be that."

i swear it so true. if i die in my sleep i want somebody to read that at my funeral for me please.thats all for now.

oi yesh thats right..they are back....now all i need is everybody but my mom to leave...i dont want anybody else around...from my family that is. they came home around 5.....i cleaned the fuck out of the house today then went to work for 3 hours....got some great songs today off the net..i missed these songs soooo fuckin much..... my favorite song by smashmouth...stoned...fuck yesh....

the epitome of my life.....i swear if you combine this song,soco amarretto lim,and lua you would have my life...... but hey o the fuck well right....im sore as hell right now,kinda pissed at miscellaneous people and tired as all hell...this week has finally caught up with me. :) i love my boyfriend....

well heres my shit from yesterday for whoever may care...most of it pplies to today as well.

*so please forgive what i have done no you cant stay mad at the setting sun i mean we all get tired i mean eventually there is nothing left to do but sleep*
i have accepted this fact and moved on.gotton the fuck over it.but what do i do now?i mean everybody needs somethin in life but what do we have when we sleep?maybe thats the point....that i can cling onto to the fact that it is all fantasy and be conforted by the fact that its all temporary.everything goes away.everything dies.nothing lasts.that scares me sometimes.i want something stable.something i can hold onto and depend on but everything goes away.'dont stay just so you can be the only one to say they never left me'...the thing that scares me most is that i do trust him and love him so much.i do depend on him.when he's not around i dont feel like me anymore.i need him more than i have ever needed anyne.even michael i knew hated me so i didnt let myself need him.he is the one who usually needed me...for grades,sex,and avoiding expulsion and whatnot.but with him its an equal thing.im so scared.scared to be alone.scared to be hurt. scared of being wrong....thinkin that its all ok.i can be around him for days and not even get remotely annoyed.i love him so fuckin much.but love can hurt you so bad as we all know.its almost like asking to get hurt.it hurts so much you think you'll die from the pain but the saddest part of all is that you dont die from it.death is so welcoming most of the time.there are few things worth living for and yet every little rock seems worth living for when he is around.he makes life ok and that scares me too.nothin comforts me as much as he does.not even the blood he took the place of.he wont let me do that anymore.understandable but it doesnt change the fact that when he isnt around i still want to....but that 'im dissappointed in you' look he gives me all the time comes into my head and it stops me.....i wake up missing him...wishing he was holding me....i dont like being alone.....he is my best friend....fuckin a  i need new meds soon....next thing ya know im gonna start writtin poems and shit.....feelin wears me out.

im feeling freakishly positive about life today.not sure why....i wrote this fat note yesterday to nobody in particular but im too lazy to write it in here right now so ill do that later but i just wanted to share my positive energy...:) sposed to go swimmin with the boy later...so yeah  who knows....i want coffee and i need a book but whatevs...life tastes good at the moment.

hmmm yeah today was wierd..i was all happa nd bouncy ALL day it was wierd...then i finally got back to me at dinner time...i hate hearing ppl chew but thats what i get with my family...i still have to sit with them even though i wont eat.

2 days without hanging out with adam..its wierd...even weirder that he is with other ppl and not me...all day.... im upbeat but sick of being home....and bitchy on the inside....i have no books to read....

have to see my dad this saturday....

also: had a fat talk with the parentals about when they are gone....i have to be home at like 9 everynight that they are gone....fuck that....

sick of worrying for no reason about a bunch of things i have no right to think about or contemplate because i mean nothing to them....and as such have no right to be involved in their lives.....fuckin a.....

ok as i was doin my math hw like a good lil kid i realized that i had been doin hella shit wrong and so i probobly failed the quiz today which sucks ass cuz i need a c in that class.....fuck ass.....oi....today was cool i guess...kinda nice and calm after school.....just came home......got in the car after a lil bit and left....did errands for my mom then i ran into adam on my way to lindz...things have been kinda tense with us lately.....i hate it....but yeah then i went to lindz and wwe walked around town for like DAYS then went back to her house and ate oreos and watched tv....it was really nice...i like the rain and we saw HELLA snails!!!i love snails...and even if we dont do anthin crazy lindz always makes me smile...oi my lil twin(who is actually taller than me)...lol....then i hope tomorrow is cool cuz megums and me are supposed to go job-ing after school which will be much fun cuz its me and meg and who the fuck couldnt have fun with us?!?!lol....

my mom leaves friday!!!!oi im sooo happy...its nice to have less ppl in the house...then saturday should be fun...even if we all just kick back....bring your own food and blankets....muahahaha

 

"do you wanna get away?get in the car we can leave today....do you wanna celebrate our just made little holiday?...and we go crazy but happy is all that you make me and everythings gonna get better baby..."

it was his grandmas birthday so we went to his uncles house at like 4.we stayed there until like 9.it was cool cuz adam has a lil 3 year old cousin aho i played with most of the night...it was kinda cute to watch adam get all jealous of a 3 year old.lol...the lil kid hugged me goodbye and adam was like"i cant watch!" oi i love that boy....tehehe and he loves me....muahahaha...ok ill stop that now......
